Well, finally the thread on Bill G wandered onto a more interesting
topic... writing macros.

> Whenever JMF wrote macros (I remember some effort for the monitor
> and he wrote the macros for my accounting project), he would
> work and work and work on them.  Invariably, he would throw up
> his hands, take a walk over to Nixon's office, and then Dave
