We were working on it in PDP-10 land.  And, despite my
self-inflicted feather in my hat, I think we were getting
pretty damn good at it.

[J_Sauter]
Could you go into detail?  Most of what you did
was after I left.  What I mean by more detail is
a list of rules that you would like to see followed
by a software development organization that wished to 
ship their product.  For example, "the linker must 
compile and link correctly using field-image software."
